# Design tokens

In `src/index.css` (`:root` + `.dark`). Use tokens — no hardcoded theme hex.

| Group | Tokens |
|-------|--------|
| Surfaces | `--go-bg` `--go-bg-card` `--go-bg-panel` `--go-bg-elevated` `--go-bg-sidebar` |
| Text | `--go-text` `--go-text-body` `--go-text-secondary` `--go-text-muted` |
| Accent | `--go-accent` `--go-accent-text` `--go-accent-soft` `--go-accent-border` (`#5E6AD2`) |
| Border | `--go-border` `--go-border-strong` `--go-border-subtle` |
| Status | `--go-success*` `--go-warning*` `--go-error*` |
| Elev | `--go-shadow-card` `--go-shadow-btn` `--go-radius` `--go-radius-card` |

Accent purple is intentional. Prefer soft panels over heavy card chrome unless interaction needs a container. Full list → `go-ui` skill or `:root` block only.
